.TH "xvip_pipeline_prepare" 9 "xvip_pipeline_prepare" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
xvip_pipeline_prepare \- Prepare the pipeline for streaming
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" xvip_pipeline_prepare
.BI "(struct xvip_pipeline *pipe "  ","
.BI "struct xvip_dma *dma "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pipe" 12
the pipeline
.IP "dma" 12
DMA engine at one end of the pipeline
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Validate the pipeline if no user exists yet, otherwise just increase the use
count.
.SH "RETURN"
0 if successful or -EPIPE if the pipeline is not valid.
